dct_title_s: Road map of Mercer County, New Jersey : Showing principal highway routes, prepared for public distribution by the Mercer County Board of Chosen Freeholders / Harry F. Harris, County Engineer. (Verso)
dct_description_sm: With (on verso): "Historical map of Mercer County" [scale approximately 1:146,215] and location map of Mercer County in New Jersey. Verso includes photographs, information on Mercer County, and "Historic Tour of Mercer County." North is oriented towards upper right of map. Map shows county road system, state highways, improved and unimproved roads, administrative boundaries.
dct_publisher_sm: New York, NY : General Drafting Co., Inc. Mapmakers, 1932.
